I'm sorry. Welcome back.

850
00:55:23,127 --> 00:55:24,082
Thanks.

851
00:55:24,847 --> 00:55:26,565
You look good.
I feel good.

852
00:55:28,327 --> 00:55:30,522
There's something
that you've got to see.

853
