a degree of regularity.

946
01:02:19,687 --> 01:02:21,279
Constance has leukaemia?

947
01:02:23,127 --> 01:02:24,446
You didn't know?

948
01:02:26,967 --> 01:02:28,002
Wait.

949
01:02:32,447 --> 01:02:33,596
No, I didn't.

950
01:02:42,687 --> 01:02:45,076
It's funny how selfish
we can be, isn't it?

951
