When I first heard Constance
was dying, I was so mad at her.

952
01:02:53,527 --> 01:02:55,245
I thought,
"How can you do this to me?

953
01:02:55,327 --> 01:02:58,478
"I mean, you know how hard
it is for me to need other people. "

954
01:03:01,247 --> 01:03:02,885
Why hadn't she told you?

955
01:03:04,927 --> 01:03:06,599
She said she was too busy.

956
01:03:09,407 --> 01:03:11,398
I guess since death
was chasing her...

957
01:03:11,487 --> 01:03:13,478
she wanted to help
other people avoid it.

958
01:03:18,287 --> 01:03:20,357
That's what she did with her life.

959
01:03:23,607 --> 01:03:28,044
Constance left this world
a better place than she found it.

960
01:03:31,407 --> 01:03:34,399
It's a small but difficult thing.
